00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:10.694
And the time has come. This is the time.

00:00:12.807 --> 00:00:14.433
The time.

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.400
It is all mentioned thousands of years back.

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:19.400
If you heard about the Bhrighumuni

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:23.527
there is written a complete book called as Nadi Granth

00:00:23.647 --> 00:00:26.776
about these times everything described, Sahaja Yoga, everything.

00:00:26.896 --> 00:00:30.760
Even, hundred years back I would say,

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:35.000
William Blake has described everything about Sahaja Yoga, everything!

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.760
But people called him crazy.

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:43.189
They liked people like Byron, all imaginary people.

00:01:01.347 --> 00:01:05.075
I don't know what to call myself. It's very difficult. (Laughter)

00:01:05.195 --> 00:01:06.800
You know what mysticism is.

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:11.880
I know. You can call Me everything I think

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:17.520
It is quite an integration of so many things I have.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:20.539
But I would like to call myself as the Mother.

00:01:20.659 --> 00:01:22.800
That's the sweetest and the best I think.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:26.323
Because I am very patient,

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:32.352
perhaps and extremely forgiving.

00:01:41.697 --> 00:01:47.150
It is a rebirth, a rebirth.

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.542
And the birth is given by the Mother only.

00:01:50.662 --> 00:01:53.190
Father can't give the birth.

00:02:00.255 --> 00:02:04.769
It is an immaculate rebirth.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.880
No I don't tell anything like that for that before that.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:19.405
But you give up yourself. I don't say this.

00:02:19.525 --> 00:02:22.446
You just give up yourself.

00:02:22.941 --> 00:02:26.293
Whatever is not good for you, just give up. Because you become joy.

00:02:26.413 --> 00:02:30.949
You start feeling the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost that gives you vibrations

00:02:31.069 --> 00:02:32.800
and you don't want to do anything like that.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:36.080
Now for example, if you ask Me to take to drugs, I will not.

00:02:36.246 --> 00:02:37.886
I mean I'm never tempted

00:02:38.006 --> 00:02:40.200
for alcohol or anything. I'm never tempted to anything.

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:42.480
I just don't get tempted to anything.

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:44.040
You just don't do it yourself

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:47.270
because if you are the spirit, you are so detached.

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:50.440
If you become the spirit, you become the glory of the spirit.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:51.960
You have the powers of the spirit.

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:55.400
You become such a great personality yourself.

00:02:55.527 --> 00:02:58.287
You just don't do it.

00:02:59.086 --> 00:03:01.373
I don't have to tell you.

00:03:01.556 --> 00:03:04.269
I don't force anything whatsoever.

00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:07.900
You become yourself. That only.

00:03:08.020 --> 00:03:12.700
When you become yourself you are great, no doubt about it.

00:03:12.820 --> 00:03:17.060
It is a very revolutionary time we are.

00:03:17.180 --> 00:03:20.969
Very revolutionary. You should see the signs of the revolution.

00:03:21.089 --> 00:03:23.280
We never had so many seekers.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:28.720
We never had so many confusions. So many problems.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:31.261
And in that confusion only,

00:03:31.403 --> 00:03:37.422
the lotus of your spirit is going to shine.
